where T cl_*[OE; O/] is (5.32) evaluated on the mean fields, and it must be recalled that G, the full connected two-point function for the \Phi field is not the inverse of G\Gamma 1 defined in eq. (5.11) when OE 6= 0.

For QED the analogous expression is

T_*(x) = T cl_*[A] \Gamma i2r(_tr nfl*)G(x; x)o \Gamma iN tfffiaeoe_* @ff@0fiDaeoe(x; x0)jx=x0

